table-fake-caption-8.title: Tables do not use `<caption>` instead of cells with the `[colspan]` attribute to indicate a caption.

[Learn more about captions](https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/4.10/table-fake-caption).

td-has-header-9.title: `<td>` elements in a large `<table>` do not have table headers.
